OL,4,Ccollapsed under its own weight
OL,6,FA council has admitted that a historic
OL,7,Fpub was demolished by mistake ` after
OL,8,Finitial claims it had collapsed.
OL,10,FThe Market Tavern in Sheffield,
OL,11,Finitially opened in 1797 and rebuilt
OL,12,Fin 1914, was due to be knocked down in
OL,13,FJanuary after becoming unsafe.
OL,15,FSheffield City Council agreed to delay
OL,16,Fthe planned demolition to allow
OL,17,Fcampaigners more time to find a way to
OL,18,Fsave it.
