OL,6,FWhen a turret later collapsed, the
OL,7,Fcouncil said it had done so under its
OL,8,Fown weight.
OL,10,FHowever, it has now said that claim
OL,11,Fwas incorrect.
OL,13,FThe council said "new information has
OL,14,Fsince come to light" showing the
OL,15,Fdemolition company was instructed "in
OL,16,Ferror" to continue.
