OL,6,FCllr Ben Miskell, chair of the
OL,7,Ftransport, regeneration and climate
OL,8,Fcommittee, said an internal
OL,9,Finvestigation would take place.
OL,11,FHe said: "The demolition of the Market
OL,12,FTavern wasn't a decision we took
OL,13,Flightly, however, given the condition
OL,14,Fof the building I am advised we were
OL,15,Fleft with no choice.
OL,17,F"As an organisation transparency is
OL,18,Fvital to us and we are sharing this
OL,19,Fupdate with our residents and
OL,20,Fstakeholders as soon as it has come to
OL,21,Flight.
