OL,6,F"Throughout the process, I have been
OL,7,Fkeen that partners are kept fully
OL,8,Finformed. I am disappointed that this
OL,9,Fdoes not appear to have been the case
OL,10,Fand people have been provided with
OL,11,Finaccurate information."
OL,13,FHallamshire Historic Buildings and
OL,14,Fheritage charity SAVE had fought
OL,15,Fagainst the proposed demolition.
OL,17,FA spokesperson told the Local
OL,18,FDemocracy Reporting Service there were
OL,19,Fstill "many unanswered questions".
